    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>I had a crazy idea the other day: I hate trying to figure out what the update hooks should be for the distributions that I manage.  So, instead of having to remember things or work hard, I'm trying to work smarter.  <a href="http://drupal.org/project/profiler_builder">Profiler Builder</a> is a module I made to help automate the installation profile / distribution production process.</p></div></div></div>
